                     <title key="work_4573">Collectiones epistolarum et evangeliorum de tempore et de sanctis</title>
                     
                     <rubric>Collectio quedam omeliarum et sermonum per totum annum</rubric>
                     <note>A lectionary for the whole year</note>
                     <note>It begins with the vigil of Christmas, 'Cernens ecclesia' (p. 9), 
                        which is preceded by a preface in a somewhat earlier hand (p. 1)</note>
                     <note>At p. 256 are additional lections for saints, martyrs, virgins, etc.</note>
                     <textLang mainLang="la">Latin</textLang>
